  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1060239">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1060239/" class="title-link">高地？什么的高地？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1060239"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1102107/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1102107-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1102107/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">ezfinance</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-07-23"
      class="main-meta">2006-07-23 22:03:28</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1060239_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  抱着挺大的兴致专门买了《高地》来看，本以为茅盾文学奖得主的作品，总是很有点看头的。不想，越看越觉得胡扯！ 一个野战军师职干部，还是所谓优秀的，竟然多年来一直沉湎于对班排战术的研究，一点没有成长成为一个战役指挥员。太令人失望了！

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1060239/#comments">(2回应)</a>
